<gidredirect oldg␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀06.0" newgid="uk.org.publicwhip/debate/2005-05-19a.306.0" matchtype="perfectmatch"/>
